ook.com/tv-shows/2019/05/27/game-of-thrones-fans-celebrating-true-mvp-andrew-mcclay/|publisher=Comicbook|title=Game of Thrones Fans Are Celebrating the Show's True MVP Andrew McClay|author=Jamie Jirak|date=2019-05-27 |accessdate=2019-05-27}}</ref>  McClay revealed in ''Game of Thrones: The Last Watch'' that his character's name in the last three seasons was Aberdall Strongbeard.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n\n* {{IMDb name|8256997}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:McClay, Andrew}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Irish male television actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century Irish male actors]]\n", "name_user": "82.4.143.248", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrew_McClay"}
