 January 2011, it is part of the town [[Jessen (Elster)]].\n\n==Geography==\nSch\u00fctzberg lies about 12&nbsp;km west of [[Jessen (Elster)|Jessen]] on the [[Elbe]].\n\n==Economy and transportation==\nFederal Highway (''Bundesstra\u00dfe'') B 187 between [[Wittenberg]] and Jessen is about 12&nbsp;km to the east.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Schutzberg}}\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Province of Saxony]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Cottbus]]\n\n\n{{Wittenberg-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sch%C3%BCtzberg"}
